r       — Percentage 0-100.\n26: #   difficulty  : enum          — trivial | easy | medium | hard | very_hard\n27: #   priority    : enum          — critical | high | medium | low | wishlist\n28: #   depends_on  : list[string]  — IDs of tasks that must complete first.\n29: #   effort      : string        — ISO 8601 duration (e.g. \"PT2H\", \"P1D\").\n30: #   started_at  : string|null   — ISO 8601 datetime or null.\n31: #   ended_at    : string|null   — ISO 8601 datetime or null.\n32: #   constraints : list[string]  — Technical or process constraints.\n33: #   forbidden   : list[string]  — Explicitly forbidden approaches.\n34: #   references  : list[string]  — URLs or file paths for relevant docs.\n35: #   notes       : list[string]  — Free-form updates (newest first).\n36: #   subtasks    : list[task]    — Always [] in folder-based storage (legacy).\n37: #   agent_type  : string|null   — Optional agent type from registry.\n38: #\n39: # =============================================================================\n40: \n41: version: \"1.0\"\n42: \n43: meta:\n44:   created_at: \"{{created_at}}\"\n45:   updated_at: \"{{updated_at}}\"\n46:   project: \"{{project}}\"\n47:   generator: \"wombo-combo\"\n48:   maintainer: \"{{maintainer}}\"\n\n(End of file - total 48 lines)\n</content>","title":"src/templates/_meta.yml","metadata":{"preview":"# =============================================================================\n# WOMBO COMBO! — Task Store Metadata (_meta.yml)\n# =============================================================================\n#\n# This file lives at: .wombo-combo/<tasks|archive>/_meta.yml\n# Sibling files: one <task-id>.yml per task (see TASK SCHEMA below).\n#\n# REQUIRED FIELDS:\n#   version    : string — Schema version (currently \"1.0\").\n#   meta       : object — Metadata about this task store.\n#     created_at  : string — ISO 8601 datetime when the store was created.\n#     updated_at  : string — ISO 8601 datetime, auto-updated on every write