{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1773437646130,"sessionID":"ses_316e48f3cffeGrhJEXdprD247G","part":{"id":"prt_ce91ee0b8002QrClgQ5If4uYVH","sessionID":"ses_316e48f3cffeGrhJEXdprD247G","messageID":"msg_ce91ed75a0010ZexSMouyCMSCx","type":"tool","callID":"toolu_vrtx_01XNEpmAJJwybVezBQL9kx24","tool":"edit","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-agent-selection-per-feature/src/lib/templates.ts","newString":"/**\n * Ensure the agent definition file exists at the expected path.\n * If missing, reinstall from the bundled generalist template and warn.\n *\n * Called at the start of `woco launch` to prevent the failure mode where\n * agents spawn without their agent definition file.\n *\n * When `agentName` is provided (from a task's `agent` field), also ensure\n * that the specified agent definition exists. For non-default agents,\n * only warns if missing (does not generate a template — the user must\n * provide custom agent definitions).\n *\n * @returns true if the default file was reinstalled, false if it already existed.\n */\nexport function ensureAgentDefinition(\n  projectRoot: string,\n  config: WomboConfig,\n  agentName?: string\n): boolean {","oldString":"/**\n * Ensure the agent definition file exists at the expected path.\n * If missing, reinstall from the bundled generalist template and warn.\n *\n * Called at the start of `woco launch` to prevent the failure mode where\n * agents spawn without their agent definition file.\n *\n * @returns true if the file was reinstalled, false if it already existed.\n */\nexport function ensureAgentDefinition(\n  projectRoot: string,\n  config: WomboConfig\n): boolean {"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","title":"src/lib/templates.ts","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/fulgidus/Documents/wt-wombo-agent-selection-per-feature/src/commands/launch.ts":[{"range":{"start":{"line":32,"character":2},"end":{"line":32,"character":19}},"message":"'areAgentDepsReady' is declared but its valu