{"type":"text","timestamp":1773437844775,"sessionID":"ses_316e48f3cffeGrhJEXdprD247G","part":{"id":"prt_ce921d44c001DzqKd1q176FiVg","sessionID":"ses_316e48f3cffeGrhJEXdprD247G","messageID":"msg_ce921cab9001t8FHlXr3bzgxSD","type":"text","text":"All 5 commits are clean and well-structured. Let me do a final summary of everything implemented:\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nAll 8 tasks completed successfully. Here's what was implemented across 5 commits:\n\n### 1. Task Schema (`src/lib/tasks.ts`)\n- Added optional `agent?: string` field to the `Task` interface\n- Documented it as referencing local agent definition files from `.opencode/agents/<agent>.md`\n- Independent of the existing `agent_type` field (external registry)\n\n### 2. Schema Validation (`src/lib/task-schema.ts`)\n- Added validation for the `agent` field in `validateTask()`\n- Checks that it's a string when present\n- Warns if the value isn't kebab-case format\n\n### 3. Task Store (`src/lib/task-store.ts`)\n- Updated `normalizeTask()` to handle null/empty `agent` values (same pattern as `agent_type`)\n\n### 4. Agent Template System (`src/lib/templates.ts`)\n- `renderAgentTemplate()` now accepts optional `agentName` parameter\n- When a non-default agent is specified, reads from `.opencode/agents/<agentName>.md` with placeholder substitution\n- Falls back to generalist template with a warning if the custom file doesn't exist\n- `ensureAgentDefinition()` now accepts optional `agentName` and warns about missing custom agent definitions\n\n### 5. CLI (`src/index.ts`)\n- Added `agent?: string` to `CLIArgs`\n- Added `--agent <name>` flag to the arg parser\n- Added help text for the new flag\n- Passes `agent` to `cmdLaunch()`\n\n### 6. Launch Command (`src/commands/launch.ts`)\n- Added `agent?: string` to `LaunchCommandOptions`\n- Agent resolution priority: CLI `--agent` flag > task-level `agent` field > registry `agent_type`\n- Checks per-task agent definitions exist after feature selection\n- Passes CLI `--agent` to `ensureAgentDefinition()` for early validation\n\n### 7. Schema Documentation (`src/templates/_meta.yml`)\n- Documented the new `agent` field in the task schema comments","time":{"start":1773437844774,"end":1773437844774}}}
